high_descs: Turn around and walk around the right side of the bed to the dresser.
Pick up the pen from the dresser.
Turn around and walk to the other end of the dresser.
Place the pen inside the black mug on the dresser.
Pick up the mug and pen from the dresser.
Turn around to the left and walk back around the bed.
Place the mug on the night stand by the bed.
anns.task_desc: Move a mug and pen to the night stand.

high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the black dresser on your left.
Pick up the leftmost red pen off of the black dresser.
Turn around and take a step forward, then turn right and walk up to the door, turn right again and walk up to the black dresser.
Put the red pen in the black mug on the dresser.
Pick up the black mug with the pen in it off of the dresser.
Walk over to the wooden nightstand to the right of the bed behind you.
Put the mug with the pen in it on the front right corner of the nightstand.
anns.task_desc: Put a mug with a pen in it on a nightstand.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the drawer
Grab the pen off of the drawer
Move slightly to the left
Put the pen in the black mug
Grab the mug off of the drawer
Turn around and go to the nightstand to the right of the bed
Put the mug on the right of the nightstand
anns.task_desc: Putting a black mug with a pen in it on a nightstand
